                    <div class="bg-white border-2 border-pink-500 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-pink-600 mt-0 flex items-center tracking-tight text-lg">👩‍🦰 女性一人で通うなら</h5>
